<HL>
   REVIEW &amp; OUTLOOK (Editorial):
   The Tsongas Difference
</HL>
<DATE>
02/20/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A14
</SO>
<CO>
   LABOR TAXES
